🔹 🎯 Task: Smart Command System

You are building a simple console command handler (like a mini terminal).

📥 Input:
String command;
⚙️ Requirements:

The system should respond to these commands:

"start" → "System starting..."
"stop" → "System stopping..."
"restart" → "Restarting system..."
"status" → "System running normally"
"help" → "Available commands: start, stop, restart, status"

⚠️ Important:

Use enhanced switch (Java 14+)

📤 Example:
Input: start
Output: System starting...